
                  ~ evee.js ~

    Tiny, modular, cross-browser, modern event
    binding micro-library with support for leakless
    data-handler binding and triggering events.
    Inspired by https://github.com/arextar/Vine.

    Example usage:

      evee.bind(el, 'click', function(ev) {
      });

      evee.unbind(el, 'click', handler);

      // simulate a cancellable mouse click
      evee.trigger(el, 'click');

                   ~ Plugins ~

    autobind.js: data binding to help include some
    data alongside your event.

      var fn = evee.au.make(function(ev) {
      }, data);
      evee.bind(el, 'click', fn);

    But wait, there's more!

      evee.au.bind(el, 'click', function(ev) {
        ev.data === data;
      }, data);

      evee.au.unbind(el, 'click', fn);

    delegate.js: Event delegation support.

      var d = new evee.delegate(el);
      d.bind('click', 'selector', function(ev) {
      });
      d.unbind('click', 'selector' [,fn]);
      d.off();

    Installation via bower:

      $ bower install eugene-eeo/evee.js
